No. 10-10011. Kevin Grant, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 931, 132 S. Ct. 371,

181 L. Ed. 2d 236,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7023, October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 636 F.3d 803.
